description: Green Impact Partners Inc., a clean energy company, provides water, waste, and solids treatment and recycling services in North America. It operates through two segments, Water and Industrial, and Energy Production. The company operates seven water and solids treatment and recycling facilities. It also acquires, develops, builds, and operates renewable natural gas (RNG) projects; and distributes RNG, biofuel, and hydrogen. It serves customers in agriculture, forestry, government, midstream, public infrastructure, oil and gas production, potash, and utilities sectors. Green Impact Partners Inc. is based in Vancouver, Canada.
